                        name "Disclosing security-related issues"
                        sub "a) issue description, vulnerability score as per CVSS or a similar system for ranking vulnerabilities, and affected product version(s); and"
                        gpt_requirement_id "IEC 62443-4-1_DM-5_a"
                        carel_description "A process shall be employed for informing product users about reportable security-related issues in supported products in a timely manner with content that includes but is not limited to the following information: a) issue description, vulnerability score as per CVSS or a similar system for ranking vulnerabilities, and affected product version(s); and"
